Package com.feilong.core.util.predicate

自定义的 Predicate,常用在 CollectionsUtil.select(java.util.Collection, org.apache.commons.collections4.Predicate), CollectionsUtil.groupCount(java.util.Collection, org.apache.commons.collections4.Predicate, String) 等地方.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayContainsPredicate<T>
    调用 PropertyUtil.getProperty(Object, String) 获得 propertyName的值,判断是否 ArrayUtils.contains(Object[], Object) 在 values数组中.
    BeanPropertyValueEqualsPredicate<T>
    调用 PropertyUtil.getProperty(Object, String) 匹配属性值.
    CollectionContainsPredicate<T>
    调用 PropertyUtil.getProperty(Object, String) 获得 propertyName的值,判断是否 Collection.contains(Object) 在 values集合中.
